{"tid":1360380,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"周博賢作歌送給年輕抗爭者：伴我行下去 多麼需要你留在大隊 藉互相補位進和退 挽手打破頑強壁壘","createTime":"2019-07-24T10:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T23:23:54.000Z","uid":277187,"like":87,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"01a8c9825443745ce34e59183df8f30036c48624","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=odCs4_8tRzs&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DodCs4_8tRzs%26feature%3Dshare&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9YTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=f92ad6c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=odCs4_8tRzs&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n《伴我行下去》周博賢<br />\n「作為一個廢老，可以做到的不多，唯有做回較擅長的，不管有沒有用。其實過去數年，相信跟許多香港人一樣，自己是陷入一種極頽和迷失的狀態。幸得今次運動中年輕人以至香港人整體所展現的團結、美麗、勇氣、智慧和決心，令我重新看到希望，也教我看到一個前所未見的香港，給我一種前所未有、以身為香港人而驕傲的自豪感。<br />\n<br />\n今次無論結果如何，我最不想見到的是年輕人純粹而美麗的靈魂，被邪惡的權力無情地扼碎。然而，每次當我出現這種擔心的時候，年輕人的表現總給我信心和驚喜；在最黑暗最醜惡的時刻，竟也看到人性最美麗和光輝的一面！<br />\n<br />\n故此，我們真的要好好行下去，留有用之軀，齊上齊落。尤其在經歷過元朗恐襲後，香港人，真的一個也不能少。」"},{"pid":"e1eacb49e9fdc85e2a575d8c831c7e71d7f2b047","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"7989742e83f6d0934066189011c5e5e96ddcd083","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:38:54.000Z","msg":"希望多D人聽到，好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f77d6febf67315c5e5796aa3cf5517f965d575","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7651862740de13a0121f7957c32867e705f1749","tid":1360380,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(呼籲!!)(汲取G20經驗)關於登報一事提升輿論問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360136</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09edd72ebf4fa598fed0d04529d659bb4945343d","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"曲／詞：周博賢<br />\n圖：周小某<br />\n結他：史彥庭@MUSZE<br />\n母帶製作：Anthony Yeung@aym<br />\n剪接：Jun Cheng<br />\n<br />\n《伴我行下去》<br />\n世界教你驚恐心碎<br />\n贈與你瓦斯加淚水<br />\n中炮處痛楚揮不去<br />\n到哪裡療傷都不對<br />\n後處似有黑影在追<br />\n怯怕到有家都歸不去<br />\n<br />\n我也試過似你這般<br />\n失去了希望<br />\n你卻教我看得到曙光<br />\n<br />\n伴我行下去<br />\n多麼需要你留在大隊<br />\n藉互相補位進和退<br />\n挽手打破頑強壁壘<br />\n伴我行下去<br />\n免我孤單去面對<br />\n<br />\n你已說過清晰的根據<br />\n亦告訴我怎可像水<br />\n愛與智慧統統傾出去<br />\n世界看似早給粉碎<br />\n幸有你變得可期許<br />\n你是暗處光輝的子女<br />\n<br />\n我也試過似你這般<br />\n失去了希望<br />\n你卻教我看得到曙光<br />\n<br />\n伴我行下去<br />\n多麼需要你留在大隊<br />\n藉互相補位進和退<br />\n挽手打破頑強壁壘<br />\n為我裝上防具，口渴送水<br />\n合力突破恐懼<br />\n<br />\n伴我行下去<br />\n多麼需要你留在大隊<br />\n藉互相補位進和退<br />\n挽手過這神奇之旅<br />\n伴我行下去<br />\n去到光輝結局裡"},{"pid":"f0bb5d6aa01051f6e87e6470cf318defa914d21f","tid":1360380,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018aeb45b1af9af7148194f7eeca60155de04f83","tid":1360380,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"佢好多歌都講社會，一直都出緊聲<img src=\"/assets